title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:var(--awb-typography1-line-height);\"><strong>Biling\u00fcismo<\/strong><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-5 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" title=\"431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n\" src=\"https:\/\/colombus.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n-1.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/colombus.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n-1.jpg\" alt class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-4999\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27960%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201280%20960%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27960%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/colombus.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n-1-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/colombus.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n-1-400x300.jpg 400w, https:\/\/colombus.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n-1-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/colombus.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n-1-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/colombus.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n-1-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/colombus.edu.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/431313882_834656705342186_3986893144435920896_n-1.jpg 1280w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-5\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abrazamos la riqueza del biling\u00fcismo como un pilar fundamental de nuestra educaci\u00f3n. Con un compromiso firme con la excelencia acad\u00e9mica y la comprensi\u00f3n intercultural que no solo enriquece las mentes de nuestros estudiantes, sino que tambi\u00e9n abre puertas hacia un mundo de oportunidades. Nuestros estudiantes se destacan en competencias comunicativas en ingl\u00e9s, prepar\u00e1ndolos para el \u00e9xito tanto en entornos laborales internacionales como en estudios intensivos. Ofrecemos diversas oportunidades para que los estudiantes demuestren su competencia a trav\u00e9s de pruebas reconocidas como las del convenio Cambridge Assessment English y obtengan las certificaciones correspondientes.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-7 fusion_builder_column_1_2 1_2 fusion-flex-column fusion-column-inner-bg-wrapper fusion-column-liftup-border\" style=\"--awb-inner-bg-color:rgba(67,85,152,0.15);--awb-inner-bg-color-hover:rgba(67,85,152,0.15);--awb-inner-bg-size:cover;--awb-inner-bg-box-shadow: 0px 0px ;;--awb-width-large:50%;--awb-margin-top-large:10px;--awb-spacing-right-large:3.84%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:10px;--awb-spacing-left-large:3.84%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\" data-scroll-devices=\"small-visibility,medium-visibility,large-visibility\"><span class=\"fusion-column-inner-bg hover-type-liftup\"><span class=\"fusion-column-anchor\"><span class=\"fusion-column-inner-bg-image\"><\/span><\/span><\/span><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-6 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:var(--awb-typography1-line-height);\">Proyectos de S\u00edntesis<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-6\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">En la fase did\u00e1ctica final de nuestro programa, fomentamos que los estudiantes desarrollen proyectos de s\u00edntesis que aborden problem\u00e1ticas relevantes en su entorno, as\u00ed como posibles soluciones. Esta etapa constituye una oportunidad invaluable para que los estudiantes pongan en pr\u00e1ctica los conocimientos adquiridos y desarrollen habilidades de an\u00e1lisis cr\u00edtico y resoluci\u00f3n de problemas. Nuestro enfoque se centra en empoderar a los estudiantes para que identifiquen problemas significativos en su entorno y propongan soluciones innovadoras y viables. Bajo el lema \u00abExplorando Horizontes\u00bb, estos proyectos son el resultado de un arduo trabajo, investigaci\u00f3n profunda y la integraci\u00f3n de m\u00faltiples disciplinas.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typo